  "read_only_context_after": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01997:202b8cf88416]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01998:ff2eb9e78880]]{note}\n固定端反射通常对应波节，自由端反射通常对应波腹。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01999:06b3847e1b6f]]{note}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02000:1ed622168fac]]",
  "read_only_context_before": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01951:37c03cd615f1]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01952:ff2eb9e78880]]{solution}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01953:e91392da46b8]] \n在左侧延长线上，点 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01954:b06e9eb4fb6b]] 到右侧波源更远，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01955:ad1112ffd0d4]]，于是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01956:ff9b956c9a18]]，对应相长干涉，合振幅为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01957:6e530814f967]]。在右侧延长线上，路程差符号反过来，[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01958:14d68fec65de]]，因此 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01959:7b5e1875dba0]]，对应相消干涉，合振幅为 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P01960:30c034f085a7]]。\n所以左侧延长线上始终加强，右侧延长线上始终减弱到完全相消。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P01961:06b3847e1b6f]]{solution}",
